{"tid":771293,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"雙胞女兒超萌正面曝光　熊黛林取名也要曬恩愛","createTime":"2018-08-08T00:05:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-08T02:35:46.000Z","uid":81228,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"fb8f4c38c313338b64b4e1a511d0e31058ecbd4a","tid":771293,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T00:05:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180807/640_cce302a33a4555754f6176b495c5ccad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180807%2F640_cce302a33a4555754f6176b495c5ccad.jpg&h=aeeb8ce0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n熊黛林（右）與老公郭可頌抱著雙胞胎女兒入鏡。翻攝熊黛林微博<br />\n<br />\n港星熊黛林昨為雙胞胎女兒舉辦百日宴，她與富商老公郭可頌抱著2位小公主亮相，萌娃首度正面照曝光，其中一位淡定看著鏡頭，眉宇神似爸爸郭可頌；另一個卻皺眉快哭的樣子，雖然是雙胞胎，但個性好像大不相同。<br />\n<br />\n熊黛林這次現身穿著紅色修身禮服，身材曲線已經恢復大半，宴會上也曝光女兒英文名字叫Kaylor與Lyvia，分別取自父母英文名的開頭字母，連取名都默默曬恩愛。（郭妤／綜合報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180807/640_f748d2eec6f857cdea0890c141a2b826.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180807%2F640_f748d2eec6f857cdea0890c141a2b826.jpg&h=4300ec2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n熊黛林（左）與老公郭可頌婚姻美滿。翻攝熊黛林微博<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180807/640_33525e7e65295c7cadbfb6986afd0bdd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180807%2F640_33525e7e65295c7cadbfb6986afd0bdd.jpg&h=67e7b0c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n熊黛林（左）與老公郭可頌婚姻美滿。翻攝熊黛林微博<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180807/640_2deb8e4a25f68e8ea91ca362b37283c7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180807%2F640_2deb8e4a25f68e8ea91ca362b37283c7.jpg&h=ddbb0d95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n熊黛林（左）與老公郭可頌為女兒取名Kaylor與Lyvia。翻攝熊黛林微博<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180807/1406324/\" da